{"author":"Sunan Abu Dawud","hadith":{"hadithnumber":1908,"arabicnumber":1908,"text":"। জা‘ফর (রহ.) থেকে একই সনদে বর্ণিত। এতে আরো আছেঃ সুতরাং তোমরা নিজ নিজ অবস্থানস্থলে কুরবানী করো।[1] সহীহ।","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Muslim (1218)"}],"reference":{"book":11,"hadith":188}}}